    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、琴乃ちゃんから誘ってくれるなんて嬉しいな～）\n（えへへ、つい気合い入れて来ちゃった）",
      "startTime": 11.2900109779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "（あ、琴乃ちゃん、もう来てる）\n（って……あれ？）",
      "startTime": 18.5000001746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ優、渚を遊びには誘ったけど\n本当にこんなことでいいの？",
      "startTime": 26.3775829019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前やん。琴乃ちゃんと過ごす時間が\n渚ちゃんには最高のプレゼントになるんよ",
      "startTime": 32.7784123576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "そこにちょちょいとスパイスを加えれば\n最高のお誕生日の思い出になるはずや",
      "startTime": 39.5117467082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "スパイス……？",
      "startTime": 43.2784131643,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10982.721443800003,
          "startTime": 54.2611346081
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ほな、うちは編集部の人達とこっそりついて行くわ\n何かあったら伝えるから、イヤホンは外さんといてな～",
      "startTime": 49.6944679415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "あ……行っちゃった\nなんだか嫌な予感がするんだけど……",
      "startTime": 60.1333326178,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3266.668224500002,
          "startTime": 63.4000008423
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "今の、優ちゃん？",
      "startTime": 63.8905212238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "わっ！？　な、渚！\nえっと、ついさっきまで一緒の仕事だったの",
      "startTime": 67.9738593414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事、終わったばっかりなんだ\n忙しい中ありがとね",
      "startTime": 75.1333326178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "う、ううん、遊びたいって言ったのは私だから\nそれじゃあ、行こっか",
      "startTime": 81.8666659512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "カレーパン、美味しかったね\nゆっくり地元を回るの、なんだか久しぶりな気がする",
      "startTime": 88.4333326178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、学校が終わったら\n最近はすぐに東京に戻らないといけなかったし",
      "startTime": 95.4666659512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そういえば、『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』\nのことなんだけど、アンケートいらなくなっちゃった",
      "startTime": 101.8333326178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "編集部の人が「こっちで考えるから楽しみにしてて」\nって言うから、お任せすることにしたの",
      "startTime": 109.0603316686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なんだ、楽しみだね",
      "startTime": 112.2461815629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一方その頃",
      "startTime": 117.4036223365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、そこは一つのパンを分け合ったりせな！\nいけ、そこや！　くぅ～、あかん、やきもきしてまう！",
      "startTime": 123.7492290616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "……もう我慢出来へん、やっぱ渚ちゃんのためにも\nうちがスパイスを加えるしかなさそうや！",
      "startTime": 133.6036194953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフさんもそう思いますよね！？　ね！？\n任せて下さい！　うちが最高の撮れ高作りますっ！",
      "startTime": 140.6369528286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "「あー、あー、こちらオペレーターの鈴村ですー\n琴乃ちゃん、聞こえてますかー、どうぞー」",
      "startTime": 151.3036194953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "――ゆ、優！？\nな、何、急に……渚に聞かれちゃうってば",
      "startTime": 156.3999886034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "「イヤホンやから大丈夫やって\nそれよりずっと陰から見てたけど、普通過ぎるで」",
      "startTime": 163.8238235942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
